戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804d271d8ed1b7517a41b73e0437188561c3ce4c","tid":271392,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T02:53:13.000Z","msg":"屌bates motel我未睇到最尾 就見到你個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e787c9291a5b8129f6155df4265c4ccf6c5d15","tid":271392,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T02:56:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌bates motel我未睇到最尾 就見到你個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我講個幕好似係s2 我冇追落去啦<br />\n但個幕真係好深刻<br />\n我代入dylan到 一開始真係憎到norma出煙<br />\n但最後個個位 Norma 肯帶埋Dylan走真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7fd13c622a1d62533668a5ff7c945f0d16090e","tid":271392,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌bates motel我未睇到最尾 就見到你個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我講個幕好似係s2 我冇追落去啦<br />\n但個幕真係好深刻<br />\n我代入dylan到 一開始真係憎到norma出煙<br />\n但最後個個位 Norma 肯帶埋Dylan走真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都